K. C. Clyde https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/K._C._Clyde 0 K.C. Clyde (born May 2, 1980) is an American actor. He lives in Los Angeles and is the son of writer and director Craig Clyde. He is a member of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints. K.C._Clyde ( born May_2_,_1980 ) is an_American_actor . He lives in Los_Angeles and is the_son of writer_and_director_Craig_Clyde .
